{"704020":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Master Arena","steam_appid":704020,"required_age":0,"is_free":true,"detailed_description":"<h1>Join our Discord<\/h1><p><a href=\"https:\/\/steamcommunity.com\/linkfilter\/?url=https:\/\/discord.gg\/x5pZay9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/704020\/extras\/join_our_discord.png?t=1656166635\" \/><\/a><\/p><br><h1>About the Game<\/h1>Master Arena is an arena shooter with fresh gameplay using a unique inventory and perks system. <br>Accessible to everyone, easy to handle, and satisfying to play. Duel, Deathmatch, Capture the Flag, Trials, and Roball, come join arenas from 2 to 10 players.<br><br>The game includes offline modes support, online dedicated servers + LAN support, and a map editor with Steam Workshop!<br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/704020\/extras\/steam_bande_perk.png?t=1656166635\" \/><br>The game can be played with a unique perks system. There are currently 9, from healing your teammates to turning invisible without forgetting flashbangs, smoke, or freon grenades.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/704020\/extras\/Perks.gif?t=1656166635\" \/><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/704020\/extras\/steam_bande_dodge.png?t=1656166635\" \/><br>Master Arena has a dodge-based movements’ gameplay. Mastering dodges and wall-dodges give you a speed advantage in jumping around maps.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/704020\/extras\/2022-05_Dodges.gif?t=1656166635\" \/><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/704020\/extras\/steam_bande_map.png?t=1656166635\" \/><br>24 maps available and more under development.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/704020\/extras\/maps.gif?t=1656166635\" \/><br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/app